Object.Field: LKM BICC to ADW Copy Direct
SNP_TRT : LKM Object Storage to ADWC Copy Direct

COMPONENT NAME: LKM BICC to ADW Copy Direct COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.2.1.4.0 or above
DESCRIPTION
This LKM will load data from BICC to Oracle Autonomous Data Warehouse. It is using dbms_cloud.copy_data() function to load data into a staging table. It has to be used in combination with Oracle or generic SQL IKM.
DESCRIPTION This LKM will load data from BICC Storage to Oracle Autonomous Data Warehouse. It is using dbms_cloud.copy_data() function. This LKM has to be used as standalone, no IKM is needed. It will load data directly into target table. Source attributes must match target column names. Either use data entities with matching attributes or set option GENERATE_FIELD_LIST = false. All target columns will be loaded, not matter whether they are mapped or not. LKM BICC to ADWC Copy Direct does not support any transformations.
If set to True ODI will submit a BICC extration job for the source datastore.
Max wait time before considering BICC job failed. Blank value means no timeout.

Specify the date of your previous load. Only extract files created after this date will be processed by the current run. Default is empty string, meaning all the extract files will be processed. Use format yyyymmdd_hh24miss. Example 20190508_182024.
